    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways? I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and looked after. It runs beautifully and is ready to hit the road today. It\u2019s got a little bit of personality from its travels, but it\u2019s a fantastic, dependable ride that won't let you down. I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have\u2014come by and take it for a test drive!",
      "price": 32000.0,
