      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. Riding on a refreshed suspension with Bilstein dampers, this driver-focused example offers exceptional turn-in and throttle steer capability. Clean title, mechanically sound, and ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Engine runs well. Maintenance records available.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear bumper\u2014typical of careful road use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features premium leather seating that has been conditioned quarterly; the driver's side bolster shows only slight creasing, while the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium surround-sound audio, are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent oil change, brake pad replacement, and a fresh alignment for the high-tread all-season tires. This car has been a reliable companion and is ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
